me keeping you to myself.

135
00:16:01,327 --> 00:16:01,793
Swallow this.

136
00:16:35,227 --> 00:16:35,784
Who are you?!

137
00:16:38,897 --> 00:16:41,695
Have I got a sight for you two.

138
00:16:43,602 --> 00:16:45,934
We've been waiting for this, Miss.

139
00:17:35,120 --> 00:17:36,212
I can't do that again.

140
00:17:38,590 --> 00:17:41,889
You reacted like you always do.

141
00:17:42,694 --> 00:17:44,594
Especially when you're with me.

142
00:17:45,864 --> 00:17:47,024
Because of the drug.

143
00:17:47,633 --> 00:17:50,261
Should I call your boyfriend next time, too?

144
00:17:55,641 --> 00:18:01,136
Lt'd be funny to tell him about
our warm little relationship.

145
00:18:02,714 --> 00:18:05,842
Next time we should try
doing it in front of him.

146
00:18:31,677 --> 00:18:35,807
You took my gun... Are you nuts?!

147
00:18:36,849 --> 00:18:38,248
Give it back.

148
00:18:46,959 --> 00:18:49,086
Are you serious, Ayana?

149
00:19:17,256 --> 00:19:18,314
You...!

150
00:19:31,603 --> 00:19:33,366
Oh, you're shittin' me...

151
00:20:08,273 --> 00:20:12,209
MYSTERIOUS EXPLOSION
ROCKS APARTMENT BUILDING!

152
00:20:12,344 --> 00:20:15,108
POLICE SUSPECT DRUG RING

153
00:20:15,247 --> 00:20:19,047
DETECTIVE KILLED IN EXPLOSION

154
00:20:23,922 --> 00:20:25,719
It's not like it was your fault.

155
00:20:26,058 --> 00:20:27,047
Don't beat yourself up over it.

156
00:20:28,093 --> 00:20:32,792
Right... Kohei, he and I...

157
00:20:34,166 --> 00:20:35,224
It's nothing.

158
00:20:36,969 --> 00:20:38,766
Thanks for coming today.

159
00:20:49,681 --> 00:20:51,273
What's keeping him?!

160
00:20:58,357 --> 00:21:00,587
So, here you are. Remember us?

161
00:21:03,595 --> 00:21:07,429
What, you can't recognize
us with our clothes on?

162
00:21:12,104 --> 00:21:14,664
This time you'll be partying with us.

163
00:21:15,407 --> 00:21:16,965
For a long, long time.

164
00:21:27,853 --> 00:21:28,319
Huh?

